              <td width="50%" valign="top" bgcolor="#FFFFFF" class="box-cont"><p><img src="images/scr-mode.png" width="108" height="22" alt="j-Hawk Script Mode" /></p>
                <p>j-Hawk provides its own scripting<br />
                  language called $hawk scripting<br />
                  where the Developer has to write<br />
